CatDescriptText: David L. Lawrence was Mayor of the City of Pittsburgh 1946-1959, Governor of Pennsylvania 1959-1963, and he died in 1966.
TitMainTitle: Group of men and women seated at long banquet table above other diners at table "6", including woman in center wearing light colored satin shirred off the shoulder dress, and Pittsburgh Mayor David L. Lawrence on far left, in Webster Hall
